<!-- doc/src/sgml/docguide.sgml -->

<appendix id="docguide">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=33df0e6ec0677d69fcd428dc1e22ab8c sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
 <title>Documentation</title>
________________________________________________________-->
 <title>文档</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=33df0e6ec0677d69fcd428dc1e22ab8c -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1728ea1c71d75e38d6c8b770a7e5bb87 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
 <para>
  <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> has four primary documentation
  formats:

  <itemizedlist>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     Plain text, for pre-installation information
    </para>
   </listitem>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     <acronym>HTML</acronym>, for on-line browsing and reference
    </para>
   </listitem>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     PDF, for printing
    </para>
   </listitem>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     man pages, for quick reference.
    </para>
   </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>

  Additionally, a number of plain-text <filename>README</filename> files can
  be found throughout the <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> source tree,
  documenting various implementation issues.
 </para>
________________________________________________________-->
 <para>
  <productname>PostgreSQL</productname>有四种主要的文档格式：

  <itemizedlist>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     纯文本，用于安装前信息
    </para>
   </listitem>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     <acronym>HTML</acronym>，用于在线浏览和参考
    </para>
   </listitem>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     PDF，用于打印
    </para>
   </listitem>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     手册页，用于快速参考
    </para>
   </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>

  另外，在<productname>PostgreSQL</productname>源码树里面还有许多纯文本风格的<filename>README</filename>文件，它们记录各种实现问题。
 </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1728ea1c71d75e38d6c8b770a7e5bb87 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=54ed0159173846bfbc174d5cfb043700 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
 <para>
  <acronym>HTML</acronym> documentation and man pages are part of a
  standard distribution and are installed by default.  PDF
  format documentation is available separately for
  download.
 </para>
________________________________________________________-->
 <para>
  <acronym>HTML</acronym>文档和手册页是标准发布的一部分并且被默认安装。PDF格式的文档可以独立地下载。
 </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=54ed0159173846bfbc174d5cfb043700 -->

 <sect1 id="docguide-docbook">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=7d7f69dac688fa5b76de910a4fc62115 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <title>DocBook</title>
________________________________________________________-->
  <title>DocBook</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=7d7f69dac688fa5b76de910a4fc62115 -->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=64490dd7408f60c410cca229105cd179 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <para>
   The documentation sources are written in
   <firstterm>DocBook</firstterm>, which is a markup language
   defined in <acronym>XML</acronym>.  In what
   follows, the terms DocBook and <acronym>XML</acronym> are both
   used, but technically they are not interchangeable.
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   文档源码是用<firstterm>DocBook</firstterm>编写的，它是一种用<acronym>XML</acronym>定义的标记语言。在下文中，虽然术语 DocBook 和<acronym>XML</acronym>都被使用，但在技术上它们是不能互换的。
  </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=64490dd7408f60c410cca229105cd179 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2dc645e1c2f706a2582a56604357b48a sig_cn_org=a71bccfdfc80cfc9fd767bc0a0a69d7e source=15.7 
  <para>
  <productname>DocBook</productname> allows an author to specify the
   structure and content of a technical document without worrying
   about presentation details.  A document style defines how that
   content is rendered into one of several final forms.  DocBook is
   maintained by the <ulink url="https://www.oasis-open.org">
   OASIS group</ulink>.  The <ulink url="https://www.oasis-open.org/docbook/">
   official DocBook site</ulink> has good introductory and reference documentation and
   a complete O'Reilly book for your online reading pleasure.  The
   <ulink url="http://newbiedoc.sourceforge.net/metadoc/docbook-guide.html">
   NewbieDoc Docbook Guide</ulink> is very helpful for beginners.
   The <ulink url="https://www.freebsd.org/docproj/">
   FreeBSD Documentation Project</ulink> also uses DocBook and has some good
   information, including a number of style guidelines that might be
   worth considering.
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
  <productname>DocBook</productname>允许作者指定技术文档的结构和内容，而不必担心呈现细节。
   文档样式定义了如何将内容呈现为几种最终形式之一。DocBook由
   <ulink url="https://www.oasis-open.org">OASIS组织</ulink>维护。
   <ulink url="https://www.oasis-open.org/docbook/">官方DocBook网站</ulink>有很好的入门和参考文档，
   还有一本完整的O'Reilly书籍供您在线阅读。对于初学者来说，
   <ulink url="http://newbiedoc.sourceforge.net/metadoc/docbook-guide.html">NewbieDoc Docbook Guide</ulink>非常有帮助。
   <ulink url="https://www.freebsd.org/docproj/">FreeBSD文档项目</ulink>也使用DocBook，并提供一些很好的信息，
   包括一些值得考虑的样式指南。
  </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2dc645e1c2f706a2582a56604357b48a -->
 </sect1>


 <sect1 id="docguide-toolsets">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6bdb5dba923ec967752d850a65b2465e sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <title>Tool Sets</title>
________________________________________________________-->
  <title>工具集</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6bdb5dba923ec967752d850a65b2465e -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2af167c7985f31dadee31fa5071f0e81 sig_cn_org=44e09ed7239645f866c93d4011680eaf source=16.8 
  <para>
   The following tools are used to process the documentation.  Some
   might be optional, as noted.

   <variablelist>
    <varlistentry id="docguide-toolsets-docbook-dtd">
     <term><ulink url="https://www.oasis-open.org/docbook/">DocBook DTD</ulink></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       This is the definition of DocBook itself.  We currently use version
       4.5; you cannot use later or earlier versions.  You need
       the <acronym>XML</acronym> variant of the DocBook DTD, not
       the <acronym>SGML</acronym> variant.
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="docguide-toolsets-docbook-xsl">
     <term><ulink url="https://github.com/docbook/wiki/wiki/DocBookXslStylesheets">DocBook XSL Stylesheets</ulink></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       These contain the processing instructions for converting the
       DocBook sources to other formats, such as
       <acronym>HTML</acronym>.
      </para>

      <para>
       The minimum required version is currently 1.77.0, but it is recommended
       to use the latest available version for best results.
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="docguide-toolsets-libxml2">
     <term><ulink url="http://xmlsoft.org/">Libxml2</ulink> for <command>xmllint</command></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       This library and the <command>xmllint</command> tool it contains are
       used for processing XML.  Many developers will already
       have <application>Libxml2</application> installed, because it is also
       used when building the PostgreSQL code.  Note, however,
       that <command>xmllint</command> might need to be installed from a
       separate subpackage.
      </para>
     </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="docguide-toolsets-libxslt">
     <term><ulink url="http://xmlsoft.org/XSLT/">Libxslt</ulink> for <command>xsltproc</command></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       <command>xsltproc</command> is an XSLT processor, that is, a program to
       convert XML to other formats using XSLT stylesheets.
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="docguide-toolsets-fop">
     <term><ulink url="https://xmlgraphics.apache.org/fop/">FOP</ulink></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       This is a program for converting, among other things, XML to PDF.
       It is needed only if you want to build the documentation in PDF format.
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   以下工具用于处理文档。一些工具可能是可选的，如注释所示。

   <variablelist>
    <varlistentry id="docguide-toolsets-docbook-dtd">
     <term><ulink url="https://www.oasis-open.org/docbook/">DocBook DTD</ulink></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       这是 DocBook 本身的定义。我们目前使用的是 4.5 版本；您不能使用更高或更低的版本。
       您需要 DocBook DTD 的<acronym>XML</acronym>变体，而不是<acronym>SGML</acronym>变体。
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="docguide-toolsets-docbook-xsl">
     <term><ulink url="https://github.com/docbook/wiki/wiki/DocBookXslStylesheets">DocBook XSL 样式表</ulink></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       这些包含将 DocBook 源文件转换为其他格式（例如<acronym>HTML</acronym>）的处理指令。
      </para>

      <para>
       当前最低要求版本是 1.77.0，但建议使用最新可用版本以获得最佳效果。
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="docguide-toolsets-libxml2">
     <term><ulink url="http://xmlsoft.org/">Libxml2</ulink> 用于 <command>xmllint</command></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       该库及其包含的<command>xmllint</command>工具用于处理 XML。许多开发者可能已经安装了
       <application>Libxml2</application>，因为它在构建 PostgreSQL 代码时也会被使用。
       但请注意，<command>xmllint</command>可能需要从一个单独的子包中安装。
      </para>
     </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="docguide-toolsets-libxslt">
     <term><ulink url="http://xmlsoft.org/XSLT/">Libxslt</ulink> 用于 <command>xsltproc</command></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       <command>xsltproc</command> 是一个 XSLT 处理器，即使用 XSLT 样式表将 XML 转换为其他格式的程序。
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="docguide-toolsets-fop">
     <term><ulink url="https://xmlgraphics.apache.org/fop/">FOP</ulink></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       这是一个用于将 XML 转换为 PDF 等格式的程序。仅当您希望以 PDF 格式构建文档时才需要它。
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
  </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2af167c7985f31dadee31fa5071f0e81 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=82e8e2c628861561ed488a8b01316c2b sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <para>
   We have documented experience with several installation methods for
   the various tools that are needed to process the documentation.
   These will be described below.  There might be some other packaged
   distributions for these tools. Please report package status to the
   documentation mailing list, and we will include that information
   here.
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   我们已经在文档中记录了几种安装处理此文档所需的各种工具的方法。它们将在下文中描述。也可能有这些工具的其他打包发布。请向文档邮件列表报告那些包的状态，我们就会在这里包括它们的信息。
  </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=82e8e2c628861561ed488a8b01316c2b -->

  <sect2 id="docguide-toolsets-inst-fedora-et-al">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=9c4191653f6e5da3f38ee3770ba99d10 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <title>Installation on Fedora, RHEL, and Derivatives</title>
________________________________________________________-->
   <title>在 Fedora、RHEL 和衍生品上安装</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=9c4191653f6e5da3f38ee3770ba99d10 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e4cc80931370d75858bc112f02dd863f sig_cn_org=f3e67618fc37e0aeb51088f4d27e4b83 source=15.7 
   <para>
    To install the required packages, use:
<programlisting>
yum install docbook-dtds docbook-style-xsl libxslt fop
</programlisting>
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    要安装所需的软件包，请使用:
<programlisting>
yum install docbook-dtds docbook-style-xsl libxslt fop
</programlisting>
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e4cc80931370d75858bc112f02dd863f -->
  </sect2>

  <sect2 id="docguide-toolsets-inst-freebsd">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=9d2aaea875d5d4eb6cc30d0d9e308c1d sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <title>Installation on FreeBSD</title>
________________________________________________________-->
   <title>在 FreeBSD 上安装</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=9d2aaea875d5d4eb6cc30d0d9e308c1d -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e63529e9646b50b33688ecb8107e7aae sig_cn_org=84ddc3b075ebe46a65728c738e60cdb3 source=15.7 
   <para>
    To install the required packages with <command>pkg</command>, use:
<programlisting>
pkg install docbook-xml docbook-xsl libxslt fop
</programlisting>
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    要使用<command>pkg</command>安装所需的软件包，请执行:
<programlisting>
pkg install docbook-xml docbook-xsl libxslt fop
</programlisting>
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e63529e9646b50b33688ecb8107e7aae -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=82d60599710e6f80d170cff0fd9764ff sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <para>
    When building the documentation from the <filename>doc</filename>
    directory you'll need to use <command>gmake</command>, because the
    makefile provided is not suitable for FreeBSD's <command>make</command>.
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    在从<filename>doc</filename>目录构建文档时，你会需要用到<command>gmake</command>，因为所提供的makefile不适合于FreeBSD的<command>make</command>。
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=82d60599710e6f80d170cff0fd9764ff -->
  </sect2>

  <sect2 id="docguide-toolsets-inst-debian">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=5ac39ac0820d17e15c4f36f175fab104 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <title>Debian Packages</title>
________________________________________________________-->
   <title>Debian 包</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=5ac39ac0820d17e15c4f36f175fab104 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=c59f3314821c1f8f3bf7ec1500362038 sig_cn_org=b8e25053f2c27722b276bedf4e6e826c source=15.7 
   <para>
    There is a full set of packages of the documentation tools
    available for <productname>Debian GNU/Linux</productname>.
    To install, simply use:
<programlisting>
apt-get install docbook-xml docbook-xsl libxml2-utils xsltproc fop
</programlisting>
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    有一整套文档工具的软件包可用于<productname>Debian GNU/Linux</productname>。
    要安装，只需使用：
<programlisting>
apt-get install docbook-xml docbook-xsl libxml2-utils xsltproc fop
</programlisting>
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c59f3314821c1f8f3bf7ec1500362038 -->
  </sect2>

  <sect2 id="docguide-toolsets-inst-macos">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6f31557cc924e8b3b1c3c873032b0e85 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <title>macOS</title>
________________________________________________________-->
   <title>macOS</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6f31557cc924e8b3b1c3c873032b0e85 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=856a601be08c5ca6c832dafccedc731c sig_cn_org=3399917d1bfe9bcfef8c1e1e53106943 source=15.7 
   <para>
    If you use MacPorts, the following will get you set up:
<programlisting>
sudo port install docbook-xml docbook-xsl-nons libxslt fop
</programlisting>
    If you use Homebrew, use this:
<programlisting>
brew install docbook docbook-xsl libxslt fop
</programlisting>
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    如果您使用MacPorts，以下步骤将帮助您设置好环境：
<programlisting>
sudo port install docbook-xml docbook-xsl-nons libxslt fop
</programlisting>
    如果您使用Homebrew，请执行以下步骤：
<programlisting>
brew install docbook docbook-xsl libxslt fop
</programlisting>
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=856a601be08c5ca6c832dafccedc731c -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=314317d991777df9e6087fbbc26ca164 sig_cn_org=abfa9ca0f9653afc0e2b6f0527f15ae2 source=15.7 
   <para>
    The Homebrew-supplied programs require the following environment variable
    to be set.  For Intel based machines, use this:
<programlisting>
export XML_CATALOG_FILES=/usr/local/etc/xml/catalog
</programlisting>
    On Apple Silicon based machines, use this:
<programlisting>
export XML_CATALOG_FILES=/opt/homebrew/etc/xml/catalog
</programlisting>
    Without it, <command>xsltproc</command> will throw errors like this:
<programlisting>
I/O error : Attempt to load network entity http://www.oasis-open.org/docbook/xml/4.5/docbookx.dtd
postgres.sgml:21: warning: failed to load external entity "http://www.oasis-open.org/docbook/xml/4.5/docbookx.dtd"
...
</programlisting>
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    Homebrew提供的程序需要设置以下环境变量。对于基于Intel的机器，请使用以下命令：
<programlisting>
export XML_CATALOG_FILES=/usr/local/etc/xml/catalog
</programlisting>
    对于基于Apple Silicon的机器，请使用以下命令：
<programlisting>
export XML_CATALOG_FILES=/opt/homebrew/etc/xml/catalog
</programlisting>
    没有设置这个环境变量，<command>xsltproc</command>会抛出类似以下错误：
<programlisting>
I/O error : Attempt to load network entity http://www.oasis-open.org/docbook/xml/4.5/docbookx.dtd
postgres.sgml:21: warning: failed to load external entity "http://www.oasis-open.org/docbook/xml/4.5/docbookx.dtd"
...
</programlisting>
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=314317d991777df9e6087fbbc26ca164 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=52ebbfe59b3b30d1392470cda0815e1a sig_cn_org=0c16abb9338ca57bf7bb2ce5eab5c3cb source=15.7 
   <para>
    While it is possible to use the Apple-provided versions
    of <command>xmllint</command> and <command>xsltproc</command>
    instead of those from MacPorts or Homebrew, you'll still need
    to install the DocBook DTD and stylesheets, and set up a catalog
    file that points to them.
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    虽然可以使用苹果提供的<command>xmllint</command>和<command>xsltproc</command>版本，
    而不是来自MacPorts或Homebrew的版本，但仍需要安装DocBook DTD和样式表，
    并设置一个指向它们的目录文件。
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=52ebbfe59b3b30d1392470cda0815e1a -->
  </sect2>

  <sect2 id="docguide-toolsets-configure">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1714c7740bc426c67e448961f8cc48e8 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <title>Detection by <command>configure</command></title>
________________________________________________________-->
   <title>用<command>configure</command>检测</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1714c7740bc426c67e448961f8cc48e8 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=4084d415d680d554817e06217f93e7ed sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <para>
   Before you can build the documentation you need to run the
   <filename>configure</filename> script, as you would when building
   the <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> programs themselves.
   Check the output near the end of the run; it should look something
   like this:
<screen>
checking for xmllint... xmllint
checking for xsltproc... xsltproc
checking for fop... fop
checking for dbtoepub... dbtoepub
</screen>
   If <filename>xmllint</filename> or <filename>xsltproc</filename> is not
   found, you will not be able to build any of the documentation.
   <filename>fop</filename> is only needed to build the documentation in
   PDF format.
   <filename>dbtoepub</filename> is only needed to build the documentation
   in EPUB format.
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   在你能编译文档之前，你需要运行<filename>configure</filename>脚本，就像你在编译<productname>PostgreSQL</productname>程序本身时所作的那样。
   检查运行末尾附近的输出;它应该看起来像这样：
<screen>
checking for xmllint... xmllint
checking for xsltproc... xsltproc
checking for fop... fop
checking for dbtoepub... dbtoepub
</screen>
   如果没有找到<filename>xmllint</filename> 或 <filename>xsltproc</filename>，你将不能构建任何文档。
   <filename>fop</filename>仅在构建PDF格式的文档时需要。
   <filename>dbtoepub</filename>仅在构建EPUB格式的文档时需要。
  </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=4084d415d680d554817e06217f93e7ed -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=624cb65e9f6d315fbb2c7031afe5d754 sig_cn_org=c9ec98b0d87b9fc5f221ed0eb6bcad8b source=15.7 
  <para>
   If necessary, you can tell <filename>configure</filename> where to find
   these programs, for example
<screen>
./configure ... XMLLINT=/opt/local/bin/xmllint ...
</screen>
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   如果需要的话，你可以告诉<filename>configure</filename>在哪里找到这些程序，例如
<screen>
./configure ... XMLLINT=/opt/local/bin/xmllint ...
</screen>
  </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=624cb65e9f6d315fbb2c7031afe5d754 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b6cb1b0f0af57dcab1ff6dd44324a383 sig_cn_org=13c5396f1855191d1115b17df6d4b647 source=16.8 
  <para>
   If you prefer to build <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> using
   Meson, instead run <command>meson setup</command> as described in
   <xref linkend="install-meson"/>, and then see
   <xref linkend="docguide-build-meson"/>.
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   如果您更喜欢使用<productname>PostgreSQL</productname>通过Meson构建，请按照
   <xref linkend="install-meson"/>中描述的运行<command>meson setup</command>，
   然后参阅<xref linkend="docguide-build-meson"/>。
  </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b6cb1b0f0af57dcab1ff6dd44324a383 -->
  </sect2>
 </sect1>

 <sect1 id="docguide-build">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=75815f73cbb5a025bda286b224a2d751 sig_cn_org=8712d57993dca1bedcc3b2d72d11b7fa source=16.8 
  <title>Building the Documentation with Make</title>
________________________________________________________-->
  <title>使用 Make 构建文档</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=75815f73cbb5a025bda286b224a2d751 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=8397cd47008562b8a1297ad666f1b838 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <para>
   Once you have everything set up, change to the directory
   <filename>doc/src/sgml</filename> and run one of the commands
   described in the following subsections to build the
   documentation. (Remember to use GNU make.)
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   一旦你把所有的东西都设置好以后，切换到<filename>doc/src/sgml</filename>目录，并且运行下面小节中介绍的命令之一就可以编译文档（记住使用 GNU make）。
  </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=8397cd47008562b8a1297ad666f1b838 -->

  <sect2 id="docguide-build-html">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=90c91f9cd903269a00e451994f1a31bd sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <title>HTML</title>
________________________________________________________-->
   <title>HTML</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=90c91f9cd903269a00e451994f1a31bd -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6e9b6b237fadab1bfd7cae94ec22f3de sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <para>
    To build the <acronym>HTML</acronym> version of the documentation:
<screen>
<prompt>doc/src/sgml$ </prompt><userinput>make html</userinput>
</screen>
    This is also the default target.  The output appears in the
    subdirectory <filename>html</filename>.
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    要编译文档的<acronym>HTML</acronym>版本：
<screen>
<prompt>doc/src/sgml$ </prompt><userinput>make html</userinput>
</screen>
    这也是默认的目标。这个命令的输出将出现在子目录<filename>html</filename>中。
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6e9b6b237fadab1bfd7cae94ec22f3de -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=87a48bedde271d34fd4636132a632d99 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <para>
    To produce HTML documentation with the stylesheet used on <ulink
    url="https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/">postgresql.org</ulink> instead of the
    default simple style use:
<screen>
<prompt>doc/src/sgml$ </prompt><userinput>make STYLE=website html</userinput>
</screen>
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    要用<ulink
    url="https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current">postgresql.org</ulink>所使用的样式表
    而不是默认的简单样式生成 HTML 文档：
<screen>
<prompt>doc/src/sgml$ </prompt><userinput>make STYLE=website html</userinput>
</screen>
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=87a48bedde271d34fd4636132a632d99 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0cbafae168dddb5ba0310ba71eb10b4d sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <para>
    If the <literal>STYLE=website</literal> option is used, the generated HTML
    files include references to stylesheets hosted on <ulink
    url="https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/">postgresql.org</ulink> and
    require network access to view.
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    如果使用<literal>STYLE=website</literal>选项，生成的 HTML 文件包括对托管在<ulink url="https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/">postgresql.org</ulink> 上的样式表的引用，需要网络访问来查看。
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=0cbafae168dddb5ba0310ba71eb10b4d -->
 </sect2>

 <sect2 id="docguide-build-manpages">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=da43be8de26580526c7c84206cd8e229 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <title>Manpages</title>
________________________________________________________-->
  <title>手册页</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=da43be8de26580526c7c84206cd8e229 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0ef08aab737f255dafc5455706bad762 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <para>
   We use the DocBook XSL stylesheets to
   convert <productname>DocBook</productname>
   <sgmltag>refentry</sgmltag> pages to *roff output suitable for man
   pages.  To create the man pages, use the command:
<screen>
<prompt>doc/src/sgml$ </prompt><userinput>make man</userinput>
</screen>
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   我们使用 DocBook XSL 样式表来把<productname>DocBook</productname>
   <sgmltag>refentry</sgmltag>页转换成适合于手册页的 *roff 输出。要创建手册页，使用命令：
<screen>
<prompt>doc/src/sgml$ </prompt><userinput>make man</userinput>
</screen>
  </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=0ef08aab737f255dafc5455706bad762 -->
 </sect2>

  <sect2 id="docguide-build-pdf">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=7141609ccbd53073264c6082fca47d7c sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <title>PDF</title>
________________________________________________________-->
   <title>PDF</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=7141609ccbd53073264c6082fca47d7c -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=5559f78a1c15fb6d50fab20d4555c218 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <para>
    To produce a PDF rendition of the documentation
    using <productname>FOP</productname>, you can use one of the following
    commands, depending on the preferred paper format:

    <itemizedlist>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       For A4 format:
<screen>
<prompt>doc/src/sgml$ </prompt><userinput>make postgres-A4.pdf</userinput>
</screen>
      </para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
      <para>
       For U.S. letter format:
<screen>
<prompt>doc/src/sgml$ </prompt><userinput>make postgres-US.pdf</userinput>
</screen>
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    要使用<productname>FOP</productname>产生文档的PDF版本，可以使用下列命令之一，取决于你喜欢的纸张格式：

    <itemizedlist>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       A4格式：
<screen>
<prompt>doc/src/sgml$ </prompt><userinput>make postgres-A4.pdf</userinput>
</screen>
      </para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
      <para>
       U.S.信纸格式：
<screen>
<prompt>doc/src/sgml$ </prompt><userinput>make postgres-US.pdf</userinput>
</screen>
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=5559f78a1c15fb6d50fab20d4555c218 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e98f779bd8bc1becb93171529a44a879 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <para>
    Because the PostgreSQL documentation is fairly
    big, <productname>FOP</productname> will require a significant amount of
    memory.  Because of that, on some systems, the build will fail with a
    memory-related error message.  This can usually be fixed by configuring
    Java heap settings in the configuration
    file <filename>~/.foprc</filename>, for example:
<programlisting>
# FOP binary distribution
FOP_OPTS='-Xmx1500m'
# Debian
JAVA_ARGS='-Xmx1500m'
# Red Hat
ADDITIONAL_FLAGS='-Xmx1500m'
</programlisting>
    There is a minimum amount of memory that is required, and to some extent
    more memory appears to make things a bit faster.  On systems with very
    little memory (less than 1 GB), the build will either be very slow due to
    swapping or will not work at all.
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    因为PostgreSQL文档很大，<productname>FOP</productname>会要求可观的内存量。因此，在一些系统上，构建过程将会由于内存相关的错误而失败。通常可以通过在配置文件<filename>~/.foprc</filename>中配置Java的堆设置来解决这类问题，例如：
<programlisting>
# FOP binary distribution
FOP_OPTS='-Xmx1500m'
# Debian
JAVA_ARGS='-Xmx1500m'
# Red Hat
ADDITIONAL_FLAGS='-Xmx1500m'
</programlisting>
    这是所要求的最小内存量，当然更多的内存会让编译过程更快一些。在内存非常小（小于1GB）的系统上，编译过程会因为磁盘交换而非常慢或者根本就不工作。
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e98f779bd8bc1becb93171529a44a879 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0ee0e73ee0e2813dece62a4f79390479 sig_cn_org=8c15d3d56d7c38bc6245c83b16e48c16 source=16.8 
   <para>
    In its default configuration <productname>FOP</productname> will emit an
    <literal>INFO</literal> message for each page. The log level can be
    changed via <filename>~/.foprc</filename>:
<programlisting>
LOGCHOICE=-Dorg.apache.commons.logging.Log=&zwsp;org.apache.commons.logging.impl.SimpleLog
LOGLEVEL=-Dorg.apache.commons.logging.simplelog.defaultlog=WARN
</programlisting>
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    在默认配置中，<productname>FOP</productname>会为每一页发出一条
    <literal>INFO</literal>消息。日志级别可以通过<filename>~/.foprc</filename>更改：
<programlisting>
LOGCHOICE=-Dorg.apache.commons.logging.Log=&zwsp;org.apache.commons.logging.impl.SimpleLog
LOGLEVEL=-Dorg.apache.commons.logging.simplelog.defaultlog=WARN
</programlisting>
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=0ee0e73ee0e2813dece62a4f79390479 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=cb6ef1d5903143c697c9657f6a7b1d46 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <para>
    Other XSL-FO processors can also be used manually, but the automated build
    process only supports FOP.
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    也可以手工使用其他XSL-FO处理器，但是自动编译过程仅支持FOP。
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=cb6ef1d5903143c697c9657f6a7b1d46 -->
  </sect2>

  <sect2 id="docguide-build-syntax-check">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=9359636e1f3536bf12b595b2abcbd1a2 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <title>Syntax Check</title>
________________________________________________________-->
   <title>语法检查</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=9359636e1f3536bf12b595b2abcbd1a2 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ab09a36c5a6bc43f8757b2fdfb04a52e sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <para>
    Building the documentation can take very long.  But there is a
    method to just check the correct syntax of the documentation
    files, which only takes a few seconds:
<screen>
<prompt>doc/src/sgml$ </prompt><userinput>make check</userinput>
</screen>
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    编译文档可能会花很长时间。但是有办法只检查文档中的语法，这个过程只需要数秒：
<screen>
<prompt>doc/src/sgml$ </prompt><userinput>make check</userinput>
</screen>
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ab09a36c5a6bc43f8757b2fdfb04a52e -->
  </sect2>
 </sect1>


 <sect1 id="docguide-build-meson">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=fa2aaa078f5150a3b658600a558b5a48 sig_cn_org=7dccd220e42df29ddf6419e04fca0576 source=16.8 
  <title>Building the Documentation with Meson</title>
________________________________________________________-->
  <title>使用Meson构建文档</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=fa2aaa078f5150a3b658600a558b5a48 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=42f7c2b22529daddde6e518d71571eb4 sig_cn_org=a8839404c1ad47ae30585bd576750cc4 source=17.5 
   <para>
    To build the documentation using Meson, change to the
    <filename>build</filename> directory before running one of these commands,
    or add <option>-C build</option> to the command.
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    要使用 Meson 构建文档，请先切换到 <filename>build</filename> 目录，
    然后运行以下命令之一，或者在命令中添加 <option>-C build</option>。
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=42f7c2b22529daddde6e518d71571eb4 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=d7fb5f222069ca6df29cabad50a5a7c8 sig_cn_org=4e2925ec4b2dab55862c47e097611abe source=17.5 
   <para>
    To build just the <acronym>HTML</acronym> version of the documentation:
<screen>
<prompt>build$ </prompt><userinput>ninja html</userinput>
</screen>
    For a list of other documentation targets see
    <xref linkend="targets-meson-documentation"/>.

    The output appears in the
    subdirectory <filename>build/doc/src/sgml</filename>.
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    构建仅<acronym>HTML</acronym>版本的文档：
<screen>
<prompt>build$ </prompt><userinput>ninja html</userinput>
</screen>
    有关其他文档目标的列表，请参见
    <xref linkend="targets-meson-documentation"/>。

    输出位于子目录
    <filename>build/doc/src/sgml</filename>。
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=d7fb5f222069ca6df29cabad50a5a7c8 -->
 </sect1>


 <sect1 id="docguide-authoring">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b0df0be01c2fe01d8a6858efecae7ff8 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <title>Documentation Authoring</title>
________________________________________________________-->
  <title>文档创作</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b0df0be01c2fe01d8a6858efecae7ff8 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b5f46f9dd8f0a8c79de9749d1d1ef762 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <para>
    The documentation sources are most conveniently modified with an editor
    that has a mode for editing XML, and even more so if it has some awareness
    of XML schema languages so that it can know about
    <productname>DocBook</productname> syntax specifically.
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    文档的源码可以很方便地用具有XML编辑模式的编辑器来修改，而如果它们懂一些XML模式语言那就更好了，那样它们就能理解专门的<productname>DocBook</productname>语法。
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b5f46f9dd8f0a8c79de9749d1d1ef762 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=fa1f917985703a6e68f8db611f73aa78 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <para>
    Note that for historical reasons the documentation source files are named
    with an extension <filename>.sgml</filename> even though they are now XML
    files.  So you might need to adjust your editor configuration to set the
    correct mode.
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    注意由于历史原因，文档源文件被命名为以扩展名<filename>.sgml</filename>结尾，尽管它们现在都是XML文件。因此你可能需要调整你的编辑器配置来设置正确的模式。
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=fa1f917985703a6e68f8db611f73aa78 -->

   <sect2 id="docguide-authoring-emacs">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=f4284e9c705afc10ae43beb9d3e0f852 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
    <title>Emacs</title>
________________________________________________________-->
    <title>Emacs</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=f4284e9c705afc10ae43beb9d3e0f852 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=011b6e5cfe2bd70db1c9f5e92ccec99a sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
    <para>
     <productname>nXML Mode</productname>, which ships with
     <productname>Emacs</productname>, is the most common mode for editing
     <acronym>XML</acronym> documents with <productname>Emacs</productname>.
     It will allow you to use <application>Emacs</application> to insert tags
     and check markup consistency, and it supports
     <productname>DocBook</productname> out of the box.  Check the <ulink
     url="https://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/manual/html_mono/nxml-mode.html">
     nXML manual</ulink> for detailed documentation.
    </para>
________________________________________________________-->
    <para>
     <productname>Emacs</productname>中自带的<productname>nXML Mode</productname>是用<productname>Emacs</productname>编辑<acronym>XML</acronym>文档最常用的模式。它允许用户使用<application>Emacs</application>插入标签并且检查标记的一致性，它还自带对<productname>DocBook</productname>的支持。详细的文档请参考<ulink url="https://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/manual/html_mono/nxml-mode.html">nXML manual</ulink>。
    </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=011b6e5cfe2bd70db1c9f5e92ccec99a -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=85de8dbe0f1d6f4cd6b99289acef544d sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
    <para>
     <filename>src/tools/editors/emacs.samples</filename> contains
     recommended settings for this mode.
    </para>
________________________________________________________-->
    <para>
     <filename>src/tools/editors/emacs.samples</filename>包含了这种模式的推荐设置。
    </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=85de8dbe0f1d6f4cd6b99289acef544d -->
   </sect2>

 </sect1>


 <sect1 id="docguide-style">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=3d0fd528b81f3875492fdae0d1692fc5 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <title>Style Guide</title>
________________________________________________________-->
  <title>样式指导</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=3d0fd528b81f3875492fdae0d1692fc5 -->

  <sect2 id="docguide-style-ref-pages">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ba0031ae87a41eeaee837a1af85096c9 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <title>Reference Pages</title>
________________________________________________________-->
   <title>参考页</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ba0031ae87a41eeaee837a1af85096c9 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2f6cfc6e02f97b40fc76b4ba57e8b20c sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <para>
    Reference pages should follow a standard layout.  This allows
    users to find the desired information more quickly, and it also
    encourages writers to document all relevant aspects of a command.
    Consistency is not only desired among
    <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> reference pages, but also
    with reference pages provided by the operating system and other
    packages.  Hence the following guidelines have been developed.
    They are for the most part consistent with similar guidelines
    established by various operating systems.
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    参考页应该遵循一种标准布局。这允许用户更快找到想要的信息，并且它也鼓励作者记录一个命令的所有相关方面。不止在<productname>PostgreSQL</productname>参考页中需要一致性，操作系统或其他包提供的参考页也需要。因此人们开发了下列方针。它们的大部分与由多个操作系统建立的类似方针保持一致。
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2f6cfc6e02f97b40fc76b4ba57e8b20c -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=29134494d4cd2141b60fc7bb5eba44a0 sig_cn_org=6e8791774bc6ed78eb99b0049bbb01d3 source=16.8 
   <para>
    Reference pages that describe executable commands should contain
    the following sections, in this order.  Sections that do not apply
    can be omitted.  Additional top-level sections should only be used
    in special circumstances; often that information belongs in the
    <quote>Usage</quote> section.

    <variablelist>
     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-name">
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    描述可执行命令的参考页面应包含以下部分，并按此顺序排列。不适用的部分
    可以省略。额外的顶级部分应仅在特殊情况下使用；通常这些信息应属于
    <quote>用法</quote>部分。

    <variablelist>
     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-name">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=29134494d4cd2141b60fc7bb5eba44a0 -->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=24ae94b4d064c42401d9aa6f4a3f6aa1 sig_cn_org=14ddc4008cfdd2cff04e39773cb90aca source=16.8 
      <term>Name</term>
________________________________________________________-->
      <term>名称</term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=24ae94b4d064c42401d9aa6f4a3f6aa1 -->
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=c2d855f1113e851ef7c856d0b7fda985 sig_cn_org=694479da22485a96943ff056ecbda691 source=16.8 
       <para>
        This section is generated automatically.  It contains the
        command name and a half-sentence summary of its functionality.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        本节是自动生成的。它包含命令名称及其功能的半句摘要。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c2d855f1113e851ef7c856d0b7fda985 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-synopsis">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=22d8373b95c97b8d4cea4ea30ad0ba31 sig_cn_org=bebed635eb5c911fc3df7fe821953d2d source=16.8 
      <term>Synopsis</term>
________________________________________________________-->
      <term>概要</term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=22d8373b95c97b8d4cea4ea30ad0ba31 -->
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0ec340653095dba55913d0f460961d97 sig_cn_org=c1434837ffbac844f3d28400556e8915 source=16.8 
       <para>
        This section contains the syntax diagram of the command.  The
        synopsis should normally not list each command-line option;
        that is done below.  Instead, list the major components of the
        command line, such as where input and output files go.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        本节包含该命令的语法图。概要通常不应列出每个命令行选项；
        这些选项将在下面列出。相反，应列出命令行的主要组成部分，
        例如输入和输出文件的位置。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=0ec340653095dba55913d0f460961d97 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-description">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=60291bb5316b2a8b4e63de0b0fc6c888 sig_cn_org=cd6336eae521597da911fa0330d52c51 source=16.8 
      <term>Description</term>
________________________________________________________-->
      <term>描述</term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=60291bb5316b2a8b4e63de0b0fc6c888 -->
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=17b5657060830c1461a8bd6a8990ae09 sig_cn_org=ae6da0b201f3bd73851d6226053d4bc7 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Several paragraphs explaining what the command does.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        几段解释该命令作用的文字。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=17b5657060830c1461a8bd6a8990ae09 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-options">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=8f06b55744ee9a322efc80c5cd6afb39 sig_cn_org=2102138b4f6d028f729bade3aaf7e6a2 source=16.8 
      <term>Options</term>
________________________________________________________-->
      <term>选项</term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=8f06b55744ee9a322efc80c5cd6afb39 -->
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1be4d767cb4678496b053c3cfebb1289 sig_cn_org=10bfc476d6c2dce56b87e3b80addf93b source=16.8 
       <para>
        A list describing each command-line option.  If there are a
        lot of options, subsections can be used.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        描述每个命令行选项的列表。如果选项很多，可以使用小节。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1be4d767cb4678496b053c3cfebb1289 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-exit-status">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=a3c154407ce90f055d7314ea43714896 sig_cn_org=a00f38c6f8fbe4dff13c4f78b6eb380a source=16.8 
      <term>Exit Status</term>
________________________________________________________-->
      <term>退出状态</term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=a3c154407ce90f055d7314ea43714896 -->
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0e0efa8e799954d39e59c04088ddc56a sig_cn_org=967e190aa757176140518ed7221dbe0d source=16.8 
       <para>
        If the program uses 0 for success and non-zero for failure,
        then you do not need to document it.  If there is a meaning
        behind the different non-zero exit codes, list them here.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        如果程序使用0表示成功，非零表示失败，
        那么您不需要对其进行文档记录。如果不同的非零退出代码有特定含义，
        请在此列出它们。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=0e0efa8e799954d39e59c04088ddc56a -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-usage">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6257bba9e590a7b68440e48886f64cb6 sig_cn_org=61cd332a49028e75b340466be48c44c2 source=16.8 
      <term>Usage</term>
________________________________________________________-->
      <term>用法</term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6257bba9e590a7b68440e48886f64cb6 -->
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=bac213177a300ed341e04f42bab37b7c sig_cn_org=524d411261b2d128ff12c66db771ed4e source=16.8 
       <para>
        Describe any sublanguage or run-time interface of the program.
        If the program is not interactive, this section can usually be
        omitted.  Otherwise, this section is a catch-all for
        describing run-time features.  Use subsections if appropriate.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        描述程序的任何子语言或运行时接口。如果程序不是交互式的，
        通常可以省略此部分。否则，此部分是用于描述运行时功能的
        综合部分。如果合适，请使用子章节。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=bac213177a300ed341e04f42bab37b7c -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-environment">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e688dd1b75ae8248949788fbaa45be17 sig_cn_org=3232beb25fdb612941e9463a5f41b641 source=16.8 
      <term>Environment</term>
________________________________________________________-->
      <term>环境</term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e688dd1b75ae8248949788fbaa45be17 -->
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ff6fa1b5d7fbe0fb96c52288b969cf55 sig_cn_org=c4a9a428334a754bff7e9c115dd44376 source=16.8 
       <para>
        List all environment variables that the program might use.
        Try to be complete; even seemingly trivial variables like
        <envar>SHELL</envar> might be of interest to the user.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        列出程序可能使用的所有环境变量。
        尽量完整；即使是像<envar>SHELL</envar>这样看似微不足道的变量，
        也可能对用户有用。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ff6fa1b5d7fbe0fb96c52288b969cf55 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-files">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2afb70c44a07aaf5821058f5021b6bac sig_cn_org=620f9b8c4682c22a063b4edc45a4035b source=16.8 
      <term>Files</term>
________________________________________________________-->
      <term>文件</term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2afb70c44a07aaf5821058f5021b6bac -->
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=f079389ea236ae6fd466809f363cdfa7 sig_cn_org=5afbda03e536b2b8891d22b63e67665e source=16.8 
       <para>
        List any files that the program might access implicitly.  That
        is, do not list input and output files that were specified on
        the command line, but list configuration files, etc.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        列出程序可能隐式访问的任何文件。也就是说，不要列出在命令行上
        指定的输入和输出文件，但要列出配置文件等。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=f079389ea236ae6fd466809f363cdfa7 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-diagnostics">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6b4a7709795558b46ed487e9e44459db sig_cn_org=a00f07e81ad0ecd2a52b0ebc6538e909 source=16.8 
      <term>Diagnostics</term>
________________________________________________________-->
      <term>诊断</term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6b4a7709795558b46ed487e9e44459db -->
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=4b2fa76e42c653cbeaadc7625f212986 sig_cn_org=3de1bbfd33d60db6c24cd2c15dd90c79 source=16.8 
       <para>
        Explain any unusual output that the program might create.
        Refrain from listing every possible error message.  This is a
        lot of work and has little use in practice.  But if, say, the
        error messages have a standard format that the user can parse,
        this would be the place to explain it.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        解释程序可能产生的任何异常输出。避免列出每一个可能的错误消息。
        这需要大量工作且在实际中用处不大。但是，如果例如错误消息具有用户
        可以解析的标准格式，那么这里将是解释它的地方。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=4b2fa76e42c653cbeaadc7625f212986 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-notes">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6510cc7b16c8d50b00f6081797c17583 sig_cn_org=87a9fd0692d01d6cd134a8beab7e12fb source=16.8 
      <term>Notes</term>
________________________________________________________-->
      <term>注释</term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6510cc7b16c8d50b00f6081797c17583 -->
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1cd145125b990f8fad1f1c6604699540 sig_cn_org=b052e796e4fd76a4f87b28f4720ef09b source=16.8 
       <para>
        Anything that doesn't fit elsewhere, but in particular bugs,
        implementation flaws, security considerations, compatibility
        issues.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        任何不适合其他地方的内容，特别是错误、实现缺陷、安全性考虑、
        兼容性问题。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1cd145125b990f8fad1f1c6604699540 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-examples">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=78489d449fb1345f5346f1ba51efc09a sig_cn_org=d99b042d37245d29c72ec0a0ed0dd46a source=16.8 
      <term>Examples</term>
________________________________________________________-->
      <term>示例</term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=78489d449fb1345f5346f1ba51efc09a -->
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=bab78514ab4402da844656f1a7a0000b sig_cn_org=523bf1a48d127afd217b997a8caa232c source=16.8 
       <para>
        Examples
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        示例
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=bab78514ab4402da844656f1a7a0000b -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-history">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0d11db18407841b7a2ef72255ea685ab sig_cn_org=d6df4c252d1ba488647faa8c21b9c4a6 source=16.8 
      <term>History</term>
________________________________________________________-->
      <term>历史</term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=0d11db18407841b7a2ef72255ea685ab -->
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e23c69a33df1e4735e64f68650dcbe5e sig_cn_org=cb911703c84dcf651b4f0e05889e68d1 source=16.8 
       <para>
        If there were some major milestones in the history of the
        program, they might be listed here.  Usually, this section can
        be omitted.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        如果程序历史中有一些重要的里程碑，它们可能会在这里列出。通常，这一部分可以省略。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e23c69a33df1e4735e64f68650dcbe5e -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-author">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=dedecfe53c80c817b7f3ecb65298cb9b sig_cn_org=751484abffd78db4e9997bf6c4c2eba1 source=16.8 
      <term>Author</term>
________________________________________________________-->
      <term>作者</term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=dedecfe53c80c817b7f3ecb65298cb9b -->
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ee2dbcddf32ff4e065c34380478fc972 sig_cn_org=60bf14bca236fc1606991062384e7b6e source=16.8 
       <para>
        Author (only used in the contrib section)
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        作者（仅用于贡献部分）
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ee2dbcddf32ff4e065c34380478fc972 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry id="docguide-style-ref-pages-see-also">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=78e1e25cec33f51c537e011b843183c0 sig_cn_org=90e5a195438394f2a451dd24cf288181 source=16.8 
      <term>See Also</term>
________________________________________________________-->
      <term>另请参阅</term>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=78e1e25cec33f51c537e011b843183c0 -->
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=4cb22cd1c349708080527cb6e91d9724 sig_cn_org=55be706e41f745aeecc16c8624b738cc source=16.8 
       <para>
        Cross-references, listed in the following order: other
        <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> command reference pages,
        <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> SQL command reference
        pages, citation of <productname>PostgreSQL</productname>
        manuals, other reference pages (e.g., operating system, other
        packages), other documentation.  Items in the same group are
        listed alphabetically.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        交叉引用，按以下顺序列出：其他
        <productname>PostgreSQL</productname>命令参考页面，
        <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> SQL命令参考页面，
        引用<productname>PostgreSQL</productname>手册，
        其他参考页面（例如，操作系统，其他软件包），
        其他文档。同一组中的项目按字母顺序排列。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=4cb22cd1c349708080527cb6e91d9724 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

    </variablelist>
   </para>

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=881b0fd7696c177cee568da3e90cbb83 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
   <para>
    Reference pages describing SQL commands should contain the
    following sections: Name, Synopsis, Description, Parameters,
    Outputs, Notes, Examples, Compatibility, History, See
    Also.  The Parameters section is like the Options section, but
    there is more freedom about which clauses of the command can be
    listed.  The Outputs section is only needed if the command returns
    something other than a default command-completion tag.  The Compatibility
    section should explain to what extent
    this command conforms to the SQL standard(s), or to which other
    database system it is compatible.  The See Also section of SQL
    commands should list SQL commands before cross-references to
    programs.
   </para>
________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    描述 SQL 命令的参考页应该包含下列小节：名称、概要、描述、参数、输出、注意、例子、兼容性、历史、另见。 用法、诊断、注意、例子、兼容性、历史、又见。参数小节类似选项小节， 但是在选择哪些子句是可列出的方面有更多自由。输出小节只有在命令返回非命令结束标签的东西时才需要。兼容性小节应该解释此命令遵循 SQL 标准的程度，或者它兼容哪种其它数据库系统。SQL 命令的另见小节应该在交叉引用其它程序之前列出 SQL 命令。
   </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=881b0fd7696c177cee568da3e90cbb83 -->
  </sect2>

 </sect1>
</appendix>
